PLEASE PUT THIS MAP ONTO YOUR SERVER(S)! IT IS GREATLY APPRECIATED IF YOU DO!!!

To install the map put it into this path:

C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\(STEAMNAME)\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

(STEAMNAME) is your username that you log into steam with.


Fixed the map now with 60 slots/spawnpoints. With new screeny too:D Hope you guys like it. Comment/Rate/Download please:D
